==Useful Info==
'''Swamp dragons''' are medium-sized dragons which breathe [[poisonous cloud]]s at you, but are otherwise less threatening than most dragons. You can usually find them in [[the Swamp]], particularly in certain Swamp:4 layouts.

Like other dragons, killing it may drop [[swamp dragon scales]] (33% chance).

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*[[Poison]] resistance takes most of the fight out of swamp dragons. If you lack this, you can stand in one of the naturally-occurring [[cloud]]s of the Swamp to be (temporarily) safe from its breath.
*Killing swamp dragons has a chance to drop swamp dragon scales, which provide rPois. Great for Swamp, [[Spider's Nest|Spider]], and [[Snake]].

==History==
*Prior to [[0.19]], this monster dropped a [[swamp dragon hide|hide]] that could be turned into [[swamp dragon armour]] with a [[scroll of enchant armour]].
